tle-template=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Від <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/zoylander\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c496c674532b808d687b89287c5d6137?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c496c674532b808d687b89287c5d6137?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/zoylander\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Ivan Gavrilov <small>(Zoylander)</small></a> о <span class=\"review-date\">13 Травня, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Cool plugin. Extra fast wordpress now ) Thank you!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">INCREDIBLE RESULTS</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 з 5 зірок\" data-title-template=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Від <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/lucasgaudette\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8715bc9e0f05ea971be4d3a63b9cc74f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8715bc9e0f05ea971be4d3a63b9cc74f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/lucasgaudette\" class=\"reviewer-name\">lucasgaudette</a> о <span class=\"review-date\">12 Травня, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I\'ve used many caching plugs. This one tops it by far. And a free CDN?! I\'ve been enjoying this plugin thoroughly and my load times are insane.\n\nGreat job you guys and thanks.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">AWESOME JOB!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 з 5 зірок\" data-title-template=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Від <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/laderiva\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b4b98502af2e11622e7015a21b51855c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b4b98502af2e11622e7015a21b51855c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/laderiva\" class=\"reviewer-name\">laderiva</a> о <span class=\"review-date\">12 Травня, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This pluggin literally saved my life, had 1 day to make a presentation for a client and his website was too slow, it was very frustrating for me because i tried tons of plugins untill i reached optimole, the website took more than 10 seconds to load and after installing optimole it was only 2 seconds, amazing job guys!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Works!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 з 5 зірок\" data-title-template=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Від <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/psytrl\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d5d1f56134ec1d1bf6ee7eb8673275fe?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d5d1f56134ec1d1bf6ee7eb8673275fe?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/psytrl\" class=\"reviewer-name\">psytrl</a> о <span class=\"review-date\">10 Травня, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Installed and using with no problems and Google Search Console is happy, too.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Works Perfectly</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 з 5 зірок\" data-title-template=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Від <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/davidkonicek\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d70c2a4f99e1607f25adaa3fc634f838?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d70c2a4f99e1607f25adaa3fc634f838?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/davidkonicek\" class=\"reviewer-name\">davidkonicek</a> о <span class=\"review-date\">5 Травня, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This plugin has been very easy to use and gives you excellent compression and speed improvements.\n\nI\'m sure any size image you upload will get compressed nicely. I usually save a JPG from Photoshop using Save for Web and 100% compression. When adding the image to a WordPress page, I simply choose the full size image no matter where it\'s being placed, and Optimole does the rest.\n\nI also used the filters, telling Optimole not to compress any PNG files with the word \"logo\" in them and they\'re left as the originals.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">breaks the complete website</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 з 5 зірок\" data-title-template=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Від <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bschelst\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/259036d45389c1be38a819b885eeeb3f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/259036d45389c1be38a819b885eeeb3f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bschelst\" class=\"reviewer-name\">bschelst</a> о <span class=\"review-date\">2 Травня, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">installed the plugin, and the whole website broke.Not 1 image loading anymore, all resulting in error 404.\nit\'s faster of course, WITHOUT ANY IMAGE.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great job</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 з 5 зірок\" data-title-template=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Від <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/rickburnettart\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a44d660fdc9e13e0766b3c41cc8ff956?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a44d660fdc9e13e0766b3c41cc8ff956?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/rickburnettart\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Hilary <small>(rickburnettart)</small></a> о <span class=\"review-date\">1 Травня, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This plugin does a great job making my site faster. I have a ton of images and before it was taking at least 15 seconds to load – way too slow. Now it\'s around 2 seconds to fully load. Awesome job. </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Excellent</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 з 5 зірок\" data-title-template=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Від <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/robopope\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/63f561fdf20d51c7ac65d8755ab4024c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/63f561fdf20d51c7ac65d8755ab4024c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/robopope\" class=\"reviewer-name\">RoboPope</a> о <span class=\"review-date\">30 Квітня, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Works very well for me</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:114:\"Automatically compress, optimize and serve scaled images along with next-gen WebP all from CloudFront CDN.&hellip;\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:54:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/optimole-wp.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:4:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"s