ack an answer in a aggresive tone that we are stil looking that (after a month Omg)\n\nThey didnt sen d me by then</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Simple to use</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 з 5 зірок\" data-title-template=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Від <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/davialves\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9e352bdf5fbda43a67bb20d986ad39cb?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9e352bdf5fbda43a67bb20d986ad39cb?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/davialves\" class=\"reviewer-name\">davialves</a> о <span class=\"review-date\">10 Травня, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I loved the plugin. Very easy to use and the translation was perfect and all pages.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Game changer!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 з 5 зірок\" data-title-template=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"s