ps.w.org/translatepress-multilingual/assets/screenshot-8.png?rev=2113591\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/translatepress-multilingual/assets/screenshot-8.png?rev=2113591\" alt=\"Menu Language Switcher\"></a><p>Menu Language Switcher</p></li></ol>\";s:7:\"reviews\";s:15038:\"<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Super smooth plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 з 5 зірок\" data-title-template=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Від <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/rememberfriends\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/24e3742a1afcd1820b3d49dcf575eca4?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/24e3742a1afcd1820b3d49dcf575eca4?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/rememberfriends\" class=\"reviewer-name\">rememberfriends</a> о <span class=\"review-date\">13 Травня, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Super smooth plugin\nHave translated a Ecommerce site with 9000 products to 6 different language automatically and the lever off deepl translation is 95% perfect.\n\nThank you for a super nice plugin and great support</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Excellent plugin and support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 з 5 зірок\" data-title-template=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Від <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/pmilusheva\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/20c06285e1c0bb59406f80fc7eca1d84?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/20c06285e1c0bb59406f80fc7eca1d84?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/pmilusheva\" class=\"reviewer-name\">pmilusheva</a> о <span class=\"review-date\">12 Травня, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">The plugin is very easy to use, 100% compatible with Elementor and the support is always there to help.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Awesome support!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 з 5 зірок\" data-title-template=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Від <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/manador\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/fd1eeb01d43092f54be05429893b06a4?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/fd1eeb01d43092f54be05429893b06a4?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/manador\" class=\"reviewer-name\">manador</a> о <span class=\"review-date\">11 Травня, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Many thanks for the great support! It\'s not often that desired adjustments are directly included in the next feature update. You have done me and the affiliatetheme users a big favor. Great! Highly recommended!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Solved my problem, but still this should not be a problem.</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"3 з 5 зірок\" data-title-template=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"3\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Від <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/webseodk\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f510b36ab82f45ce6beaa115f9910193?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f510b36ab82f45ce6beaa115f9910193?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/webseodk\" class=\"reviewer-name\">webseodk</a> о <span class=\"review-date\">28 Квітня, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">My main language is Danish so all my website is coded in Danish, and i choose Danish to be my main language and still it translate my Danish to Danish somehow, so now all my text on my website text in Danish is like baby language, I see i lost a lot of organic traffic because of this and that means i\'m losing customers and money. \n\n\nThey tried to help me by making a custom plugins called:\n\n\"TP - Exclude gettext strings on default language\"\n\nI recently updated my Translatepress and now my whole website is bugged, i had to uninstall this plugin i got made, now my original text is messed up again to baby language.\n\n\nUPDATE!!\nThey now helped me make a updated version of \n\"TP - Exclude gettext strings on default language\" Plugin\nI am very thankful for that, but this function should be part of the translatepress plugin long ago, it will probably break again when future updates come, if they dont choose to implement this function into the main plugin</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Issue with Program - Strings</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 з 5 зірок\" data-title-template=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Від <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/acaccese07\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c3a0a181089e80f163bb99e04dbca411?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c3a0a181089e80f163bb99e04dbca411?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/acaccese07\" class=\"reviewer-name\">acaccese07</a> о <span class=\"review-date\">18 Квітня, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Hello, great program you have BUT\ni recently updated my wordpress to 5.4 including this program, i lost all my translation\'s on a certain page and when i click on translate page on the page im working it, it says loading strings (waited almost 2 hours and nothing happen) and never loads. I cant edit anything!\n\nAny help?</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great plugin, easy to setup and works with our Google cloud account to translate</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 з 5 зірок\" data-title-template=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Від <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/pablogil\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/75cfb3d00bc9cf53c61038c2d8dd178c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/75cfb3d00bc9cf53c61038c2d8dd178c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/pablogil\" class=\"reviewer-name\">pablogil</a> о <span class=\"review-date\">15 Квітня, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">this plugin saved us a lot of time.  We used it to automatically translate our website using our google cloud translate api account.  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great plugin!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 з 5 зірок\" data-title-template=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Від <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/aviancato\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c7ae016aa618d32b7537c527ec9464c9?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c7ae016aa618d32b7537c527ec9464c9?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/aviancato\" class=\"reviewer-name\">aviancato</a> о <span class=\"review-date\">11 Квітня, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Thank you! Easy to use and better thank the other plugin</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Best on the market!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 з 5 зірок\" data-title-template=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons